      action.witness.computeRoot(action.value.add(action.increment)),
      state
    )
  },
  initial
);
```
Something along these lines where `MyStruct` has, for a specific leaf, a witness, the current value which will compute the state root hash (on chain, not in the reducer at stage `i`), and the increment by which to change the value?
